Chapter 2: Project Structure
Use-Case and Class Diagram for the Invoicing App:

classDiagram
    class User {
        +signUp()
        +addDetails()
        +uploadLogo()
    }

    class Invoice {
        +generate()
        +calculateVAT()
    }

    class Admin {
        +login()
        +viewUsers()
    }

    class App {
        +accessWithoutRegistration()
    }

    User -- Invoice : Generates
    Admin --> User : Monitors


Use-Case and Class Diagram for the Messaging App:

classDiagram
    class User {
        +signUp()
        +addDetails()
        +sendMessage()
        +receiveMessage()
        +viewStatus()
    }

    class Message {
        +send()
        +receive()
        +encrypt()
    }

    class Contacts {
        +viewOnlineStatus()
        +findUser()
        +initiateConversation()
    }

    User -- Message : Sends & Receives
    User -- Contacts : Has & Interacts
